{
  "texts": [
    "In this research question, our goal is to assess whether our approach performs effectively when applied to various types of LLMs and when utilizing new data from a different dataset.",
    "The reason this evaluation is that given the rapid development of large models, a method must be effective across different large models.",
    "Furthermore, while our approach performs well on our dataset, it is meaningful to test it in different scenarios since the data within the same dataset may exhibit some similarities.",
    "Method.In this research question, we evaluate our framework's performance on four popular LLMs: GPT-3.5 [30], GPT-4 [31], Vicuna-13B [37], and LLama-13B [29].",
    "To mirror real-world scenarios, we use the default settings of these LLMs, including temperature and top-p values, for response generation."
  ]
}